name: The Shanghainese Girl trapped in the Flat
description: The youth of the China are powerful, indeed. They are absorbed in this history that is China, this painting, this scroll. To learn a different language, to escape to Berlin. To leave the family, to get away from the Monkey King. So many things stir inside of her. Original oil on canvas, Shanghai 2018. www.BigComicArt.com
